If your Microsoft Internet Explorer
browser was failing the [tracking protection
test](http://www.aloodo.org/test/), please <a
href="javascript:window.external.msAddTrackingProtectionList('http://easylist-msie.adblockplus.org/easyprivacy.tpl',
'EasyPrivacy Tracking Protection List')">Subscribe
to the EasyPrivacy Tracking Protection List</a>
and try again.  Aloodo is in EasyPrivacy as of today.

Tracking Protection Lists are a low-profile,
but effective, way to help protect yourself from
third-party tracking, and help protect the web sites
you use from data leakage and fraud.

If you use a different browser,
check the [list of tracking protection
options](http://www.aloodo.org/protection/) to find
something that works for you.  **EasyPrivacy is
a project affiliated with EasyList and AdBlock
Plus, but neither AdBlock Plus nor EasyList
provides tracking protection by default ([more
info](https://easylist.adblockplus.org/en/)).**
AdBlock Plus users should still run a [tracking
protection test](http://www.aloodo.org/test/) to
check the configuration.

Internet Explorer users: <a
href="javascript:window.external.msAddTrackingProtectionList('http://easylist-msie.adblockplus.org/easyprivacy.tpl',
'EasyPrivacy Tracking Protection List')">Subscribe
to the EasyPrivacy Tracking Protection List.</a>



